### 1. 회원가입 (Register)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "stats-test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Stats Tester"
}

### 2. 로그인 및 토큰 발급 (Login)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "stats-test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.accessToken);
    client.log("Token: " + response.body.accessToken);
%}

### 3. 데이터 주입 - 1일차 (Inject Data Day 1)
# 2024-12-01: 5000 steps, 3km, 200kcal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/health/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recordkey": "stats-test-user",
  "data": {
    "entries": [
      {
        "period": { "from": "2024-12-01 10:00:00" },
        "steps": 5000,
        "distance": { "value": 3.0, "unit": "km" },
        "calories": { "value": 200, "unit": "kcal" }
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 4. 데이터 주입 - 2일차 (Inject Data Day 2)
# 2024-12-02: 7000 steps, 5km, 350kcal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/health/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recordkey": "stats-test-user",
  "data": {
    "entries": [
      {
        "period": { "from": "2024-12-02 10:00:00" },
        "steps": 7000,
        "distance": { "value": 5.0, "unit": "km" },
        "calories": { "value": 350, "unit": "kcal" }
      }
    ]
  }
}

### 5. 일별 통계 조회 (Get Daily Stats)
# Expected:
# 2024-12-01: 5000
# 2024-12-02: 7000
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats/daily/7836887b-b12a-440f-af0f-851546504b13
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 6. 월별 통계 조회 (Get Monthly Stats)
# Expected:
# 2024-12: 12000 (5000 + 7000)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/stats/monthly/7836887b-b12a-440f-af0f-851546504b13
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
